---
import ProjectLayout from '../../layouts/ProjectLayout.astro';
---

<ProjectLayout
  title="FolGPT"
  period="Jun to Jul 2023"
  tags={['Flask', 'GPT-4', 'Azure Cognitive Services', 'JavaScript', 'Python']}
  github="https://github.com/eralds/folGPT"
  description="A web-based multilanguage voice assistant that supports conversation in 100+ languages using GPT-4 and Azure Speech APIs."
>
  <div class="space-y-10 text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
    <div>
      <h2 style="font-family: 'Inter Tight', Inter, sans-serif;" class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Overview</h2>
      <p>
        FolGPT is a voice-first conversational assistant for the web. The key differentiator is its multilanguage support:
        it can hold conversations in over 100 locales, including many languages that have no existing voice assistant support
        (e.g., Albanian, Swahili, and dozens of other underrepresented languages).
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4">
        The project was built to demonstrate how off-the-shelf APIs can be combined to rapidly prototype a production-like
        voice assistant with minimal custom ML work, relying instead on GPT-4 for reasoning and Azure for speech.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 style="font-family: 'Inter Tight', Inter, sans-serif;" class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">How It Works</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        {[
          { step: '1', label: 'Audio capture', desc: 'User speaks into the browser. Audio is captured via Web APIs.' },
          { step: '2', label: 'Speech to text', desc: 'Audio is sent to Azure Cognitive Services, which transcribes it in the detected language.' },
          { step: '3', label: 'GPT-4 response', desc: 'The transcript is sent to GPT-4 via the OpenAI API, which generates a contextual reply.' },
          { step: '4', label: 'Text to speech', desc: 'The reply is converted back to speech by Azure TTS and played in the browser.' },
        ].map(({ step, label, desc }) => (
          <div class="flex gap-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
            <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-sm font-bold text-accent">{step}</span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-0.5">{label}</p>
              <p class="text-sm">{desc}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 style="font-family: 'Inter Tight', Inter, sans-serif;" class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Tech Stack</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        {[
          { label: 'Backend', value: 'Flask (Python)' },
          { label: 'AI / LLM', value: 'OpenAI GPT-4 API' },
          { label: 'Speech', value: 'Azure Cognitive Services (STT + TTS)' },
          { label: 'Frontend', value: 'JavaScript, HTML, CSS' },
          { label: 'Languages', value: '100+ locales supported' },
          { label: 'License', value: 'MIT' },
        ].map(({ label, value }) => (
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-100 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-1">{label}</p>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-800">{value}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</ProjectLayout>
